{"tid":166740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"靠你們這群黃屍廢青的素質就想造王, 跟小孩玩泥沙沒多樣的","createTime":"2017-03-22T10:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T15:53:20.000Z","uid":93380,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfebc9a797ccb1480c26823618bacbafa3c45b5f","tid":166740,"uid":93380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"為了所謂的&quot;造王&quot;, 不昔把反對&quot;薯片&quot;的打成敵人/中共的人, 還談什麼民主派? 不如叫&quot;肥佬黎派&quot;吧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肥佬黎 李柱銘這些所謂的&quot;民主派&quot;領袖, 公開把&quot;民主派&quot; 的不支持&quot;薯片&quot;的人全說成內鬼, 天天說誰是內鬼誰是中共的人, 我看見也見笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我很想說呀, 共產黨做滲透工作的早就做好啦, 前後左右都是中共的人, 捉什麼?  共產黨也不會做得像你們哪麼低能. 共產黨捉內鬼, 是不會讓大眾知道, 要是你知道那代表快完結了; 在報紙上談誰是內鬼, 跟哪個自稱 &quot;國師&quot; 的面書式皇天擊殺 有什麼區別? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 看見也醉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n香港需要的是藍色力量, 愛中國, 愛中國香港的力量, 請支持林鄭做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反對黃皮白心曾俊華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da2769786776c05cbe305903174cfe10a2bfdfe","tid":166740,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"支那人死全家"},{"pid":"a1b51a99cd4b813bb7d147f117b6a219677f3dbc","tid":166740,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:07:54.000Z","msg":"五毛又夠鐘開工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f9bbd22aec825f9ae0307ce7bc016be1ba261b","tid":166740,"uid":93380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五毛又夠鐘開工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我是中國香港人, 是愛國中堅份子<br />\n你這隻畜生, 你也是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be835084ddae3d7bab890112edff1bc4eae3e6ef